                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="s1" value="STEP 1 — User fills the receipt form and clicks &quot;Create receipt&quot;" style="rounded=0;fillColor=#1565C0;strokeColor=none;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=left;spacingLeft=14;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="136" width="1040" height="26" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n1" value="The form fields are stored in React state (useState):&#10;  supplierId, reference, note — header fields (all optional)&#10;  parts[] — array of { item_id, location_id, quantity, price, currency_code }&#10;Each dropdown is populated by a React Query hook that fetches from the backend:&#10;  Supplier &lt;Select&gt; ← useSuppliers() → GET /api/suppliers (📄 queries.ts:121)&#10;  Part Number picker ← useItems() → GET /api/items (📄 queries.ts:67)&#10;  Location picker ← useLocations() → GET /api/locations (📄 queries.ts:128)&#10;Receipt form also has &quot;New Part&quot; and &quot;New Location&quot; buttons that open modals&#10;  to create items/locations inline (📄 AddReceiptForm.tsx : lines 210-219).&#10;Location is NOT auto-populated (unlike Sale form) — user must select manually.&#10;Unit Cost supports comma decimals: &quot;1,50&quot; → 1.50 (line 37, 50).&#10;📄 AddReceiptForm.tsx : lines 78-90, 109-121, 159" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E3F2FD;strokeColor=#1565C0;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="270" y="176" width="480" height="175" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n1b" value="User clicks &quot;Create receipt&quot; → form onSubmit fires handleSubmit(e)&#10;📄 AddReceiptForm.tsx : lines 159, 225" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E3F2FD;strokeColor=#1565C0;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;dashed=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="310" y="371" width="400" height="42" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="s2" value="STEP 2 — handleSubmit validates the form (AddReceiptForm.tsx lines 123-126)" style="rounded=0;fillColor=#2E7D32;strokeColor=none;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=left;spacingLeft=14;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="433" width="1040" height="26" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n2" value="e.preventDefault() — stops the browser from reloading the page.&#10;setShowErrors(true) — enables red borders on invalid fields.&#10;📄 AddReceiptForm.tsx : lines 124-125" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#2E7D32;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="310" y="479" width="400" height="50" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n3" value="if (!validation.isValid) return; — checks useMemo validation (lines 92-99).&#10;For each part, getPartLineFieldErrors() (lines 23-43) checks:&#10;  item_id must be non-empty, location_id must be non-empty,&#10;  quantity: parseInt must be finite and ≥ 1,&#10;  price (unit_cost): parseFloat(price.replace(&quot;,&quot;,&quot;.&quot;)) must be finite and ≥ 0.&#10;If any fail → function returns early, user sees red borders + error text.&#10;📄 AddReceiptForm.tsx : lines 23-43, 92-99, 126" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#2E7D32;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="280" y="549" width="460" height="100" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="d1" value="validation&#10;.isValid?" style="rhombus;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFFDE7;strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="420" y="669" width="180" height="80" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="e1" value="Validation fails — returns early. Red borders + &quot;Missing: [fields]&quot; text.&#10;User stays on form, must fix and retry.&#10;📄 AddReceiptForm.tsx : line 126 | PartLineCard.tsx : lines 56, 66-68" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFEBEE;strokeColor=#C62828;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="50" y="674" width="280" height="55" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="s3" value="STEP 3 — Build the payload and call the API (AddReceiptForm.tsx lines 128-137)" style="rounded=0;fillColor=#2E7D32;strokeColor=none;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=left;spacingLeft=14;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="769" width="1040" height="26" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n4" value="Line 128: Maps each part via partLineToInput() (lines 45-53):&#10;  { item_id, location_id, quantity: parseInt(...,10), unit_cost: parseFloat(price.replace(&quot;,&quot;,&quot;.&quot;)), currency_code }&#10;📄 AddReceiptForm.tsx : lines 45-53, 128" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#2E7D32;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="290" y="815" width="440" height="50" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n5" value="Lines 130-137: await addReceipt.mutateAsync({&#10;  receipt: { supplier_id || undefined, reference.trim() || undefined, note.trim() || undefined },&#10;  lines&#10;})&#10;  addReceipt is useAddReceipt() — a useMutation wrapping api.post(&quot;/receipts&quot;, ...).&#10;📄 AddReceiptForm.tsx : lines 130-137&#10;→ useAddReceipt at mutations.ts : lines 26-42&#10;→ api.post at api.ts : line 33" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E8F5E9;strokeColor=#2E7D32;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="280" y="885" width="460" height="118" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="s4" value="STEP 4 — apiFetch sends the HTTP request (api.ts lines 5-23)" style="rounded=0;fillColor=#E65100;strokeColor=none;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=left;spacingLeft=14;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="1023" width="1040" height="26" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n6" value="Line 6: Gets Bearer token from supabase.auth.getSession() (localStorage).&#10;Lines 8-15: Sends the HTTP request:&#10;  POST ${VITE_API_URL}/receipts&#10;  Headers: Content-Type: application/json, Authorization: Bearer &lt;token&gt;&#10;  Body: { receipt: { supplier_id?, reference?, note? }, lines: [{item_id, location_id, quantity, unit_cost, currency_code}...] }&#10;Lines 17-19: If !res.ok → throws new Error(body.error || &quot;Request failed&quot;)&#10;Line 22: If res.ok → returns parsed JSON.&#10;📄 api.ts : lines 5-23" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFF3E0;strokeColor=#E65100;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="280" y="1069" width="460" height="118" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="en" value="NETWORK ERROR — fetch() throws.&#10;Caught by useMutation onError:&#10;  toast.error(&quot;Failed to add receipt: ...&quot;)&#10;📄 mutations.ts : lines 38-40" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFEBEE;strokeColor=#C62828;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="-110" y="1096" width="200" height="64" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="s5" value="STEP 5 — Backend authenticates, then validates (receipts.py line 34, schemas.py lines 86-102)" style="rounded=0;fillColor=#4A148C;strokeColor=none;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=left;spacingLeft=14;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="1207" width="1040" height="26" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n7" value="FastAPI matches POST /api/receipts/ → create_receipt(body, user).&#10;Depends(get_current_user) runs first — extracts Bearer token,&#10;calls supabase.auth.get_user(token) to verify, loads user profile.&#10;📄 receipts.py : lines 33-34 | auth.py : lines 23-57" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#EDE7F6;strokeColor=#4A148C;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="300" y="1253" width="420" height="64" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="d2" value="Token&#10;valid?" style="rhombus;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFFDE7;strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="420" y="1337" width="180" height="80" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="e2" value="Missing/invalid/expired token → HTTPException(401)&#10;📄 auth.py : lines 28, 33, 37, 60-63" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFEBEE;strokeColor=#C62828;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="50" y="1347" width="270" height="42" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n8" value="Pydantic auto-validates JSON body against CreateReceiptRequest:&#10;  receipt: ReceiptInput (supplier_id: str|None, reference: str|None max 255, note: str|None max 1000)&#10;  lines: list[ReceiptLineInput] (item_id: str, location_id: str, quantity: int gt 0,&#10;         unit_cost: float ge 0, currency_code: str 1-10 chars)&#10;📄 schemas.py : lines 86-102" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#EDE7F6;strokeColor=#4A148C;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="290" y="1437" width="440" height="78" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="d3" value="Pydantic&#10;valid?" style="rhombus;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFFDE7;strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="420" y="1535" width="180" height="80" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="e3" value="ValidationError → HTTP 400: { error: &quot;Validation failed&quot;, details: [...] }&#10;📄 errors.py : lines 39-41" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFEBEE;strokeColor=#C62828;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="50" y="1545" width="270" height="42" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="s6" value="STEP 6 — Service → Repository → Database RPC (receipts.py:35, receipt.py:21, receipt.py:83, SQL:1-38)" style="rounded=0;fillColor=#4A148C;strokeColor=none;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=left;spacingLeft=14;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="1635" width="1040" height="26" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n9" value="Router calls service.create_receipt(body.receipt.model_dump(), [line.model_dump() ...])&#10;  model_dump() converts Pydantic models to plain dicts.&#10;📄 receipts.py : lines 35-38" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#EDE7F6;strokeColor=#4A148C;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="310" y="1681" width="400" height="50" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n10" value="ReceiptService.create_receipt delegates to self.repo.create(receipt_data, lines_data)&#10;📄 services/receipt.py : lines 21-22" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#EDE7F6;strokeColor=#4A148C;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="310" y="1751" width="400" height="42" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n11" value="ReceiptRepository.create calls the PostgreSQL RPC:&#10;  supabase.rpc(&quot;create_receipt&quot;, { p_receipt: receipt, p_lines: lines }).execute()&#10;📄 repositories/receipt.py : lines 83-87" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#EDE7F6;strokeColor=#4A148C;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="300" y="1813" width="420" height="50" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="s7" value="STEP 7 — create_receipt RPC runs in the database (SQL lines 1-38)" style="rounded=0;fillColor=#0D47A1;strokeColor=none;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=left;spacingLeft=14;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="1883" width="1040" height="26" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n12" value="PL/pgSQL function — runs as one atomic transaction:&#10;  Line 13: INSERT INTO receipts (supplier_id, reference, note)&#10;    → RETURNING receipt_id INTO v_receipt_id&#10;  Lines 21-32: FOR EACH line in p_lines:&#10;    INSERT INTO receipt_lines (receipt_line_id, receipt_id, item_id, location_id, quantity, unit_cost, currency_code)&#10;  Line 35: SELECT to_jsonb(r.*) → returns the created receipt row&#10;📄 20260402_create_receipt_sale_rpcs.sql : lines 1-38" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E3F2FD;strokeColor=#0D47A1;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="280" y="1929" width="460" height="100" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="d4" value="DB insert&#10;succeeds?" style="rhombus;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=10;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFFDE7;strokeColor=#F9A825;strokeWidth=2;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="420" y="2049" width="180" height="80" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="e4" value="FK violation (invalid item_id/location_id/supplier_id) or constraint error.&#10;general_error_handler maps PG codes → 409 &quot;Referenced record does not exist&quot;&#10;📄 errors.py : lines 28-32, 44-53" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFEBEE;strokeColor=#C62828;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="50" y="2049" width="280" height="55" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n13" value="DB triggers fire after each receipt_lines INSERT:&#10;  create_movement_from_receipt_line → INSERT INTO inventory_movements (type=RECEIPT)&#10;  apply_inventory_movement_to_balances → INCREMENT inventory_balances.quantity_on_hand&#10;All runs inside the same atomic transaction." style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#E3F2FD;strokeColor=#0D47A1;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="290" y="2149" width="440" height="64" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n14" value="RPC returns created receipt row as jsonb → HTTP 201 Created back to browser.&#10;📄 receipts.py : line 33 (status_code=201)" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#EDE7F6;strokeColor=#4A148C;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="310" y="2233" width="400" height="42" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="err" value="All backend errors (400/401/409) return as HTTP error JSON" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFEBEE;strokeColor=#C62828;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="50" y="2149" width="220" height="35" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="s8" value="STEP 8 — Response arrives back in the browser" style="rounded=0;fillColor=#2E7D32;strokeColor=none;fontSize=11;fontStyle=1;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#FFFFFF;align=left;spacingLeft=14;verticalAlign=middle;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="40" y="2295" width="1040" height="26" as="geometry"/>
                </mxCell>
                <mxCell id="n15" value="apiFetch receives the HTTP response.&#10;📄 api.ts : line 8" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;fontSize=9;fontFamily=Helvetica;fontColor=#1a1a1a;fillColor=#FFF3E0;strokeColor=#E65100;strokeWidth=2;align=left;spacingLeft=6;shadow=1;" parent="1" vertex="1">
                    <mxGeometry x="340" y="2341" width="340" height="30" as="geometry"/>
